channel.title: I am new help me!
channel.description: Alright I do not know how to get on another server besides hybridscape. I entered the IP and port, but all it does is say the server might be down press "cancel" and then "start server" to create your own. I just want to get into another person's server, but how???

item.title: I am new help me!
item.dc:creator: @I_Br3ndan_I I Br3ndan I
item.description:
@I_Br3ndan_I wrote:

First of all, I’d like to say;Welcome to MoparScape.

To login to someone’s server, you simply have to do the following.

1st.
Type in the IP, this can be done by clicking next to ‘Server IP:’ and then typing it in. Server IP’s can be found here.

2nd.
Type in any desired username and password, try to use a different password than you’re others, such as you’re RuneScape password.

3rd.
Change the port if necessary. This can be done by going to File, which is found in the top-left hand corner of the MoparScape client, then clicking on it. A small window should pop up, type in the port there. When you go to MoparScape, the default port is 43594, so if someone’s port is 43594, there isn’t any need to change it.

I hope I helped.
